<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Creative Tech raised.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Creative Tech raised.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- CS First Boston said it upgraded Creative Technology Ltd to strong buy from buy.</p>
<p>-- Further details were not immediately available.</p>
<p>-- The stock was up 1/8 to 13-5/8 in early trading.</p>
